skye mccole bartusiak ( september 28 , 1992 – july 19 , 2014 ) was an american film and television actress . she appeared in the patriot ( 2000 ) , do n't say a word ( 2001 ) , as rose wilder in beyond the prairie : the true story of laura ingalls wilder ( 2002 ) , 24 ( 2002 – 03 ) , boogeyman ( 2005 ) , and kill your darlings ( 2006 ) . mccole bartusiak died at age 21 in her apartment behind her parents ' home . her death was ruled the result of an accidental drug overdose .